    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in truly pristine shape\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just left the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and it's been meticulously maintained. It drives like an absolute dream and doesn't have a single blemish on it. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new without the brand-new sticker price, this is definitely the one for you. Feel free to reach out if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 44500.0,
